# Pulumi
Pulumi.*.yaml
!Pulumi.yaml
# The dev stack config IS committed: CI runs `pulumi up` and needs it, and its
# secret values are Pulumi-encrypted (`secure:` blobs, safe to commit) or held
# out-of-band in Secret Manager. Verify there are no PLAINTEXT secrets before
# committing infra/Pulumi.dev.yaml.
!Pulumi.dev.yaml
.pulumi/

# Firebase CLI deploy cache (firebase.json is committed)
.firebase/
